ppmtotim - complex tim creation utility
Copyright (C) 1997,1998,1999,2000 by Daniel Balster <dbalster@psxdev.de>

PPMTOTIM converts a PPM input file to a TIM output file.

- you can use an external palette
- you can use an external STP plane bitmap
- multipalette is possible

files can be pipelined, i.e.

cat input.ppm | ppmquant 16 | ppmtotim --4-bit > output.tim

